::Reptilica::

Reptilica opens his mouth, forcing himself to speak in a controlled voice, 
even though he was sweating a few gallons a minute.

"Well," he says nervioustly, "My leader's Zardus, of the Alliance. I think 
we're the dominant faction.. Our base is not on this continent, its way to 
the east. Terra's at war here. There are maybe factions," he sounded like an 
idiot, and knew it, "Most of them at civil war. The Alliance is keeping 
itself steady though..."

He gulps, hoping that he'd live to forget about this meeting.
